oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jarrett, Ted; Country Music Hall of Fame & Museum (Nashville, Tenn.); Hebb, Bobby; Howard, Frank; Jones, Johnny; Nelson, Tracy; Scruggs, Chris; Valentines (Musical group);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and gold on white) announcing Ted Jarrett Day, featuring performances by Levert Allison, Rev. Melvin Bufford, Dynamic Dixie Travelers, Earl Gaines Band, Bobby Hebb, Frank Howard, Rufus Hunter, Marion James, Johnny Jones, Carolyn Mathis, Tracy Nelson, James Nixon, Chris Scruggs, Valentines, Charles Walkers, and Joel Wright, at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on December 3.
